---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn more about Yabood and the person behind the blog">
  <Header />

  <main id="main" class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <Prose>
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <p>
        Welcome to my corner of the internet! I'm Yousif Abood, a passionate developer and
        technology enthusiast.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Do</h2>

      <p>
        I specialize in building modern web applications and exploring the latest technologies. My
        journey in software development has taken me through various languages, frameworks, and
        paradigms, always with a focus on creating elegant solutions to complex problems.
      </p>

      <h3>Areas of Interest</h3>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Web Development</strong>: Building responsive, accessible, and performant web
          applications
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cloud Architecture</strong>: Designing scalable and reliable cloud-native
          solutions
        </li>
        <li><strong>Open Source</strong>: Contributing to and maintaining open-source projects</li>
        <li>
          <strong>Technical Writing</strong>: Sharing knowledge through blog posts and documentation
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why This Blog?</h2>

      <p>This blog serves as a platform to:</p>

      <ol>
        <li>Share technical insights and tutorials</li>
        <li>Document my learning journey</li>
        <li>Connect with fellow developers and creators</li>
        <li>Contribute to the developer community</li>
      </ol>

      <div
        class="my-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-light bg-accent-light/10 p-6 dark:border-accent-dark dark:bg-accent-dark/10">
        <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-accent-dark dark:text-accent-light">
          Let's Connect!
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers and creators. Feel free to
          reach out through my social channels or drop me a message on the <a href="/contact"
            >contact page</a
          >.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>Technical Stack</h2>

      <p>Here are some of the technologies I work with regularly:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Languages</strong>: TypeScript, JavaScript, Python, Go</li>
        <li><strong>Frontend</strong>: React, Vue, Astro, Next.js</li>
        <li><strong>Backend</strong>: Node.js, Express, FastAPI</li>
        <li><strong>Databases</strong>: PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis</li>
        <li><strong>Cloud</strong>: AWS, Google Cloud, Vercel</li>
        <li><strong>Tools</strong>: Docker, Kubernetes, GitHub Actions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Beyond Code</h2>

      <p>When I'm not coding, you can find me:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>Exploring new technologies and frameworks</li>
        <li>Contributing to open-source projects</li>
        <li>Reading technical books and research papers</li>
        <li>Enjoying a good cup of coffee â˜•</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Thank you for visiting, and I hope you find the content here helpful and inspiring!</p>
    </Prose>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
